Keeping everyting in mind we need to understand Internet for our clear and better understanding. 
Internet is very vast and leans on a very big entity. It is the connection of billions of networks to form a better ecosystem where we can access all the data throughout the globe. 
Internet can break down into Inter - Net which means interconnection of data, Servers, files, computers/ smart devices. It is  also called as Networks of Networks. Where in 1960's when US forces wanted to share their data they builded a system which can where they can share information in the form of packets
